readme:
# setRobot bundle

![](http://i.imgur.com/oi9Kzk2.gif)

*Shortlink https://git.io/v7Ntn*

## Table of Contents
 - [Description](#description)
 - [Introduction](#introduction)
 - [Basic Usage](#basic-usage)
 - [Contribute](#contribute)
 - [Related Links](#related-links)
 - [Credits](#credits)
 - [License](#license)

## Description
setRobot bundle enables you to use setRobot functions quickly with best practices according to the setRobot team, as we are currently in beta if you find some bug please open a issue or make a pull request.

Note: This package is not intended to be used without setRobot, if you’d like to know what is setRobot, please refer to this [link](https://github.com/3runoDesign/setRobot) for more information.
# Introduction
This package supports `blade.php` files for now, but later we will support some others to, if you’d like to contribute just open a pull request or a issue!
## Basic usage
In a supported template file just start typing `@` then hit `CTRL + SPACE`, all the available functions will be shown, choose a function then hit enter and replace the example data with your own.
## Contribute
[#1](https://github.com/gabriellacerda/setRobot-bundle/issues/1)
### Related links
[Official setRobot Repository](https://github.com/3runoDesign/setRobot) - [Official plugin Repository](https://github.com/gabriellacerda/setRobot-bundle) - [Official plugin api Repository](https://github.com/gabriellacerda/setRobot-bundle-api)
